# Install and quickstart
SteelThread relies on access to agent activity in Portia cloud (queries, plans, plan runs). You will need a `PORTIA_API_KEY` to get started. Head over to (<a href="https://app.portialabs.ai" target="_blank">**app.portialabs.ai â†—**</a>) and navigate to the `Manage API keys` tab from the left hand nav. There you can generate a new API key.
:::tip[For a deeper dive]
Below takes you through install and two end-to-end examples. If you wanted to get a deeper understanding, head over to:
* [Streams page](/streams).
* [Evals page](/evals).
:::

## Install using your framework of choice

<Tabs groupId="installer">
    <TabItem value="pip" label="pip" default>
    ```bash
    pip install steel-thread
    ```
    </TabItem>
    <TabItem value="poetry" label="poetry">
